4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive bootcamp to become a Machine Learning Engineer. Designed for beginners, the program spans 16 weeks and includes 3 classes weekly with a maximum of 12 students per class. The course covers Python, SQL, Streamlit, and Statistics, focusing on predictive modeling and real-world applications. Students tackle supervised and unsupervised learning challenges while following a project lifecycle. Instructors include experienced professionals with advanced degrees in AI and Data Science. Certificates are recognized by multiple organizations. The course is available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop